improved_metadata.title: Spray Foam Party
improved_metadata.description: A humorous hip-hop track celebrating the life of spray foam insulation workers, featuring Snoop Dogg. It's about working hard, staying true, and enjoying life in the spray foam game.
improved_metadata.key_lyrics: It's nothing but a spray-foam party
